title: Tesla випустила ексклюзивні дошки для серфінгу
200 досок для серфинга Tesla продали за 15 часов
description: Компания Илона Маска Tesla выпускает не только электокары, но и самые разные брендированные вещи.

title: Tesla released a $1500 surfboard, and it sold out in a matter of hours
description: Tesla debuted a new product on Saturday night, in the form of a perfectly normal surfboard.
author: Emily Nicolle

title: Tesla briefly offered a $1500 surfboard
description: Elon Musk has come up withs some interesting merchandise to promote his companies: he sold Boring Company hats and then a branded flame thrower. Yesterday, his electric car company Tesla released a new product: a $1500 surfboard.
author: Andrew Liptak

title: Twitter bo blokiral račun, če boste ime spremenili v »Elon Musk«
description: Elon Musk je na twitterju med bolj dejavnimi  in priljubljenimi. To so začeli spretno izkoriščati tudi nepridipravi, ki so se pojavili po objavah šefa avtomobilskega podjetja Tesla in vesoljskega...
author: Saša Senica

title: Earnings Watch: Even Apple takes a back seat to Elon Musk right now
description: Both Apple and Tesla Inc. are set to report earnings this coming week, but the car maker’s release is likely to steal the show.
author: Emily Bary

title: Le nouveau produit Tesla est… une planche de surf !
description: Tout est bon pour faire un peu de trésorerie. Après la mini station de recharge pour mobile, le lancement flamme, la nouvelle idée d'Elon Musk : une planche de surf.
author: Vincent Bouvier

title: A Tesla csinált 200 szörfdeszkát
description: A Tesla csinált 200 szörfdeszkát - Darabját 1500 dollárért árulták, mind elfogyott.
author: Domschitz Mátyás

title: Karşınızda Tesla'nın sınırlı sayıda üretmiş olduğu karbon fiber sörf tahtaları
description: Tesla Motors, dünyaca ünlü sörf tahtası üreticisi Lost Surfboards ile iş birliği yaparak sörf tahtası üretmeye başladığını duyurdu. Tesla Surfboard 1500 dolara alıcıyla buluşacak.
author: Zeynep Yolcu
